{"tid":1685500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[法律JJ]禁制令與基本法第27條","createTime":"2019-10-31T14:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T14:55:17.000Z","uid":311223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9fdd77210349a69cb99549f6a35c54ed583e221e","tid":1685500,"uid":311223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T14:45:53.000Z","msg":"今次個禁制令有冇同基本法27條互相抵觸？<br />\n<br />\n根據基本法第27條:<br />\n<br />\n第二十七條 <br />\n香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/pda/tc/basiclawtext/chapter_3.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.basiclaw.gov.hk%2Fpda%2Ftc%2Fbasiclawtext%2Fchapter_3.html&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=e7688444\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/pda/tc/basiclawtext/chapter_3.html</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇法律界巴絲一齊探討下？"},{"pid":"2e9f15006a5417a145bd14c25d68b26d0ded8386","tid":1685500,"uid":15603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T14:49:41.000Z","msg":"講左好撚多次自由唔是絕對<br />\n諗到點樣唔是絕對既前題下禁制令侵害到人權再講<br />\n1）define點先為之足夠既人權保障<br />\n2）有左scope再拗<br />\n<br />\n即係禁連登禁telegram散播xyz言論點樣侵害人權到一個地步連minimum protection條線都低過"},{"pid":"287cb13a0d6548d09a34485855e32fc6aba19aa9","tid":1685500,"uid":113929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T14:54:14.000Z","msg":"Basic law話中央唔可以有駐港機構，而家咪有中聯辦。立法要經過立法會，再通知全國人大，但又咪通過緊急法。中央至特區政府跟本自己破壞一国兩制同基本法在先<br />\n利申：無讀過law,只係考過 care"},{"pid":"0c1e192f3d5cb46b18797a7b8d1da110dea92450","tid":1685500,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T14:55:17.000Z","msg":"冇, 法律只係黑狗既廁紙"}]}